OL,4,Cpublic sector pay rises
OL,6,FRachel Reeves said a decision will be
OL,7,Fmade soon amid reports of a
OL,8,Frecommended 5.5% rise for teachers and
OL,9,FNHS staff
OL,11,FChancellor Rachel Reeves has said the
OL,12,Fgovernment will "make sure the sums
OL,13,Fadd up" if public sector workers are
OL,14,Fgiven above inflation pay rises.
OL,16,FReports which first appeared in The
OL,17,FTimes suggest independent pay review
OL,18,Fbodies have recommended the 5.5% rise
OL,19,Ffor teachers and around 1.3 million
OL,20,FNHS staff.
