OL,6,FShe also said the government would
OL,7,Fcarry out a review of pensions to help
OL,8,Fstimulate growth by unlocking cash in
OL,9,Fschemes.
OL,11,F"People who make sacrifices and save
OL,12,Fevery month to put something aside for
OL,13,Ftheir retirement, they deserve better
OL,14,Fthan the returns they're getting on
OL,15,Fthose savings today," she said, adding
OL,16,Fthere was an "urgency" from the
OL,17,Fgovernment to unlock investment.
